name: OS-AmberGlow
description:
in my attempts to make a 'realistic' model i trained 6 different models with various different settings and merged them to "perfection", focusing on a variety of things, like nature, natural landscapes, great lighting and high detail, architectural photography and of course beautiful men and women.


-model is indeed not perfect lol

-faces tend to get weird the further away they are, usually fix it with upscale or inpainting.

-Most previews are upscaled because thats how i get best results

i tend to use Dped upscaler for most images, it works wonders with portraits and lighting/reflections
as with all my models, feel free to make your own merges using this model!

Happy Pride Month!
~enjoy <3
